Transcription.Text: "I Suddenly felt lonely. My maid is out." She laught. "I found I was out of cigarettes too! Perhaps I smoke too much!" It was the opening for a little discussion on the minor vices, as two shipboard companions might talk while occupying long chairs side by side.
